    <item>
      <title>利比亚政治危机解决后，OPEC石油产量回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/opec-s-oil-output-recovers-after-libya-resolves-political-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利比亚恢复了因短暂的政治危机而停止的石油生产，上个月欧佩克的石油产量有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/opec-s-oil-output-recovers-after-libya-resolves-political-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 14:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的里德：收益率曲线并不能带来太多收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/rieder-not-a-lot-of-money-to-be-made-in-yield-curve-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球固定收益首席投资官 Rick Rieder 在“彭博未平仓合约”上分享了他对收益率曲线的看法，他表示：“我发现今天的收益非常诱人，你可以获得大量的收益。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-01/rieder-not-a-lot-of-money-to-be-made-in-yield-curve-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:58:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶选民将决定为学校发行创纪录的 90 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/la-voters-to-decide-on-record-9-billion-of-bonds-for-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶联合学区是美国第二大学区，该学区正在请求当地选民下周批准出售 90 亿美元的学校建设债券，以在入学人数下降和城市预算压力下对老化的设施进行现代化改造。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/la-voters-to-decide-on-record-9-billion-of-bonds-for-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率上升推动收入增长，尼日利亚顶级银行股价有望上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/nigeria-s-guaranty-trust-zenith-seen-rallying-on-higher-rates</link>
