    <item>
      <title>KKR 预计数据中心繁荣将带来每年 2500 亿美元的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/data-center-boom-seen-fueling-250-billion-of-annual-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 称，支持人工智能和云计算的数据中心需求飙升，将使全球在该领域的支出增至每年 2500 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/data-center-boom-seen-fueling-250-billion-of-annual-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据失真助长美联储降息预期，美国国债价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/treasuries-soar-as-distorted-us-jobs-data-fuels-bets-on-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上个月风暴和罢工事件导致美国经济仅创造了 12,000 个就业岗位，且市场对美联储下周降息的预期保持不变，美国政府债务出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/treasuries-soar-as-distorted-us-jobs-data-fuels-bets-on-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着私人贷款需求飙升，Ares 扩大现金池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/ares-grows-cash-pool-as-demand-for-private-lending-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第三季度，Ares Management Corp. 的资产管理规模增至 4640 亿美元，比去年同期增长 17%，这得益于其美国直接贷款基金的兴趣以及最近的私募股权收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/ares-grows-cash-pool-as-demand-for-private-lending-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 11:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称伊朗计划通过代理人攻击以色列，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称伊朗可能准备在未来几天从伊拉克领土袭击以色列，油价因此上涨，市场将注意力重新转移到中东地区可能爆发的敌对行动上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 23:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
